co.cask.cdap.internal.io

Class AbstractFieldAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.internal.io.AbstractFieldAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldAccessor

    public abstract class AbstractFieldAccessor
extends Object
implements FieldAccessor
    A base implementation of FieldAccessor that throws UnsupportedOperationException for all getter/setter methods, which are meant to be overridden by children class.
